2008-03-27  Aleksander Morgado Juez  <aleksander@es.gnu.org>

	* src/base/pdf-text.c (pdf_text_transform_he_to_unicode_encoding): Use
	`PDF_TEXT_BIG_ENDIAN' from`config.h' to check host endianness.

